## What is Solid Cable?

Solid Cable is Rails 8's default WebSocket solution for Action Cable. It uses your database instead of Redis.

**Key Benefits:**
- ✅ No Redis dependency
- ✅ Uses database for pub/sub
- ✅ Real-time bidirectional communication
- ✅ Works with all Rails features
- ✅ Supports presence, typing indicators, live updates
- ✅ Works with PostgreSQL, MySQL (with polling)

